verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Through You I can do anything, I can do all things
Cause its you who gives me strength, nothing is impossible
Through you, blind eyes are open, Strongholds are broken
I am living by faith, nothing is impossible

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
I'm not gonna live by what I see,
I'm not gonna live by what I feel

verse.name: p1
verse.lines:
Deep down I, Know that You're here with me
I know that, You can do anything

verse.name: b1
verse.lines:
I believe, I believe,
I believe, I believe in You x2
